snippet.title: RUSHAWAY - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2091540/RUSHAWAY

RUSHAWAY is a 2.5D fast-paced single-player platformer, where your objective is to find the fastest ways towards the goal. Explore different paths for every level, and discover the more optimal ones, avoiding or exploiting different hazards.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Ninestudiosgame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Rushaway-113799376708365
